<bibRefCitation id="DCBF9E0EB64F378E02288A0F27282A3A" author="Vega, AS" journalOrPublisher="Gayana Botanica" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" pagination="31 - 35" refId="B282" refString="Vega, AS, de Agrasar, ZER, 2013. Lectotypifications in taxa of the genera Calamagrostis, Deyeuxia, and Digitaria (Poaceae). Gayana Botanica 70: 31 - 35" title="Lectotypifications in taxa of the genera Calamagrostis, Deyeuxia, and Digitaria (Poaceae)." volume="70" year="2013">Vega and de Agrasar 2013</bibRefCitation>
